#### Multimodal Pipeline Example (ImageToTextPipeline)
**File**: `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775497356287-4npke2/src/pipelines.js` (lines 1943-2005)

