**Key fields**:
- `tokenizer`: (Optional) AutoTokenizer class for text processing
- `model`: Model class(es) - can be single class or array `[Class1, Class2]` (tries each until success)
- `processor`: (Optional) AutoProcessor for preprocessing images/audio
- `pipeline`: The pipeline class itself
- `default.model`: Default model ID if none specified
- `type`: `"text"`, `"image"`, `"audio"`, or `"multimodal"`

**Optional features**:
- `TASK_ALIASES`: Maps aliases to base tasks (e.g., "sentiment-analysis" → "text-classification")
